                <note rend="inline" type="source">411.12/946: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Ambassador in Mexico</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Morrow</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1929-08-07T17:00:00-04:00"
                            >August 7, 1929—5 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>435. Your 306, August 6, 7 p.m. Paragraph one satisfactory.</p>
                <p>Paragraph two satisfactory.</p>
                <p>Your form letter satisfactory excepting substitute for word “implementing” the
                    words “carrying out”. Submit text thus amended to Estrada.</p>
                <p>Paragraph four satisfactory.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Cotton</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
